@startuml NL2SQL-Query-Flow
!theme plain

title NL2SQL 查询时序图 - NL2SQL Query Sequence

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceStyle arrow
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #F57F17

' === Participants ===
actor User as "用户"
participant Dashboard as "Dashboard\n(React)"
participant APIServer as "API Proxy\n(Node.js)"
participant OperatorAgent as "OperatorAgent\n(Python)"
participant NL2SQLCtrl as "Nl2SqlController\n(Java)"
participant SqlCoderSvc as "SqlCoderService\n(Java)"
participant SqlExecSvc as "SqlExecutorService\n(Java)"
participant MySQL as "MySQL\nDatabase"
participant SQLCoder as "SQLCoder\n(LLM)"

' === Auto-number ===
autonumber 1.1

' === Main Flow ===
User -> Dashboard : 输入自然语言查询
activate User
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> APIServer : POST /api/nl2sql/query
activate APIServer

APIServer -> OperatorAgent : HTTP POST
activate OperatorAgent

OperatorAgent -> OperatorAgent : Intent Detection\n(LLM)
note right
  **意图识别**
  判断为 nl2sql 意图
end note

OperatorAgent -> OperatorAgent : 构造 NL2SQL 请求
OperatorAgent -> NL2SQLCtrl : POST /api/v1/nl2sql/query
activate NL2SQLCtrl

NL2SQLCtrl -> SqlCoderSvc : generateSql(nl2sqlRequest)
activate SqlCoderSvc

SqlCoderSvc -> SQLCoder : POST /v1/completions
note right
  **LLM 调用**
  生成 SQL 语句
end note
activate SQLCoder
SQLCoder --> SqlCoderSvc : Generated SQL
deactivate SQLCoder

SqlCoderSvc --> NL2SQLCtrl : SQL 语句
deactivate SqlCoderSvc

NL2SQLCtrl -> SqlExecSvc : executeQuery(sql, maxResults)
activate SqlExecSvc

SqlExecSvc -> MySQL : SELECT query
note right
  **JDBC 执行**
  参数化查询防注入
end note
activate MySQL
MySQL --> SqlExecSvc : ResultSet
deactivate MySQL

SqlExecSvc --> NL2SQLCtrl : 查询结果
deactivate SqlExecSvc

NL2SQLCtrl --> OperatorAgent : JSON Response
deactivate NL2SQLCtrl

OperatorAgent -> OperatorAgent : 处理响应\n生成自然语言回答
OperatorAgent --> APIServer : Agent Response
deactivate OperatorAgent

APIServer --> Dashboard : HTTP Response
deactivate APIServer

Dashboard -> Dashboard : 渲染结果\n展示图表/表格
Dashboard -> User : 显示查询结果
deactivate Dashboard
deactivate User

' === Error Handling ===
note over User, SQLCoder #FFEBEE
  **错误处理路径**
  如果任何步骤失败，将返回错误信息给用户
end note

@enduml